法让其他司机接收到「我要减速了」的信息。 以上是我的想法，那么把动能回收做成松油门的设计而不是踩刹车的设计，是故意而为之还是技术条件导致的，这么设计的考虑又是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-efb51bb08ea0f4f7eed0ffd3ee0eec82_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "74 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/362638993"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4It47kpaeU8IoVEAMaCDQyODY1MzQ2IKD8g/AFMAU4WUAYcgkzNjI2Mzg5OTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1651970517.8509893", "card_id": "Q_529970143", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 59}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么最近发布的手机都开始搭载「双芯」？单芯就无法实现该有的性能吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "是否也说明目前市面芯片的拉垮？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-6bf8eaf7770fa8185a54d11550bffa21_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/529970143"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It47kpaeU8IoVEAMaCDgwMDUzMjY2IOKGmpMGMAE4pQFAGXIJNTI5OTcwMTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1651970517.8514943", "card_id": "Q_479101320", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 100}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些描写光阴的诗句，流传千年，堪称人间绝句？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我先打个样，「人生如逆旅，我亦是行人」——苏轼；今人不见古时月，今月曾照古时人。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-aff7a70ecf0a48b0a65da9bd34843849_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479101320"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It47kpaeU8IoVEAMaCDY4NzQ4MTkyIIPzz4gGMAE4zgdAGnIJNDc5MTAxMzIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1651970517.8520048", "card_id": "Q_531548935", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 157}